                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Choose the best solution per domain. A specialised mental health system alongside a home care planning tool alongside a telemonitoring solution. CareHub ensures they work together.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-xl p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-3">Wegiz-compliant by design</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">All connections in the CareHub ecosystem use FHIR and HL7. You automatically meet the Wegiz requirements without additional investment.</p>
                    </div>
